@endnode

@NODE "Regi" "Registration"

 @{b}Registration@{ub}
 ------------

 Easyplay is Shareware. To ease your decision wheather to pay or not the
 unregistered version hasn't got any limitiations ;)

 Registered users receive a personal keyfile (well, actually they don't but
 it sounded so cool to say :) ).

 How to become a registered user ?
 The simple way is to fill in the file "OrderForm", to print it out,
 sign it (in this order, if possible), put it in an envelope together
 with the registration fee and send it to @{"me" LINK "Auth"}. I won't accept 
 order forms which are not signed.
 I wonder what those orderforms look like. :)
 
 If you for any reason would like this piece of software then please send
 me some money or maybe something you have done. (On your computer that is).
 If you do so I promise to send you an update of Picture Bender as soon as
 I have done one. (If ever happens.:)
@ENDNODE

